---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Careers at Cyberfyx | Join Our Security & IT Team"
  description="Join our team of cybersecurity experts, consultants, and IT management professionals solving mission-critical security challenges."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-hero-layout" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
        <div class="fade-up">
          <div class="eyebrow">Careers</div>
          <h1>Join Our Team at <span class="text-gradient">Cyberfyx</span></h1>
          <p class="lede">We're hiring security professionals, consultants, and IT specialists to help organizations protect their digital future. Join our growing team and make a real impact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Join Us -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <h2>Why Work at <span class="text-gradient">Cyberfyx</span>?</h2>
        <p>We're more than just a cybersecurity company; we're a place where talented people solve real problems.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="gap: 2rem;">
        <div class="glass-card fade-up">
          <h3>Mission-Critical Work</h3>
          <p>Your work directly impacts organizations' security posture. You'll solve real challenges, not just perform routine tasks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100">
          <h3>Growth Opportunities</h3>
          <p>We invest in your professional development through certifications, training, and exposure to diverse security domains and technologies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-200">
          <h3>Expert Team</h3>
          <p>Work alongside security experts, architects, and thought leaders who are passionate about cybersecurity and willing to mentor.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-300">
          <h3>Competitive Benefits</h3>
          <p>Competitive salary, health insurance, continuous learning budget, and a supportive work environment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100">
          <h3>Diverse Sectors</h3>
          <p>Work across healthcare, finance, manufacturing, government, and more; each sector brings unique security challenges.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-200">
          <h3>Culture of Excellence</h3>
          <p>We value expertise, collaboration, innovation, and integrity. We're building a team that sets industry standards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Open Positions -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <h2>Open <span class="text-gradient">Positions</span></h2>
        <p>We're actively hiring for the following roles.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-2" style="gap: 2rem;">
        <div class="glass-card fade-up">
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Consulting</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Senior Security Consultant</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Lead security assessments, compliance implementations, and advisory engagements. You'll work with C-suite executives to shape organizational security strategies.</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>8+ years security/compliance experience</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>ISO 27001/NIST/PCI-DSS expertise</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Strong communication skills</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:careers@cyberfyx.net" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Apply</a>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100">
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Engineering</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Endpoint Management Engineer</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Design and deploy UEM solutions for enterprise clients. You'll configure, test, and optimize endpoint management platforms at scale.</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>5+ years endpoint/UEM experience</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Intune, MobileIron, or similar platform expertise</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Scripting and automation skills</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:careers@cyberfyx.net" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Apply</a>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-200">
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Security Services</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Penetration Tester</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Conduct security assessments, perform penetration tests, and develop detailed reports with actionable remediation recommendations.</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>CEH, OSCP, or similar certification</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>3+ years penetration testing experience</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Knowledge of offensive security tools</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:careers@cyberfyx.net" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Apply</a>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-300">
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Operations</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Security Operations Analyst</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Monitor security events, investigate incidents, and provide recommendations for security improvements. You'll be our eyes and ears 24/7.</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>2+ years SOC/Security operations experience</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>SIEM platform knowledge</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check" style="color: var(--accent-secondary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Incident handling experience</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:careers@cyberfyx.net" class="btn btn-outline" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">Apply</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Application Info -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-secondary); text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fade-up">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Don't See Your Role?</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">If you're a talented security professional or IT expert interested in joining our team, we'd love to hear from you. Send us your resume and what you're passionate about.</p>
        <a href="mailto:careers@cyberfyx.net" class="btn btn-primary hero-btn" style="min-width: 220px; padding: 1rem 2rem;">
          <span>Send Your Resume</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
